Job Description
Share
A VVIP family in Dubai is searching for a Female Personal Chef to join their household.
Desired Candidate Profile
The family is looking at either a Sous Chef or Chef de Partie from an established hotel and familiar with European dishes as well as healthy meal options. The family also places a great emphasis on cleanliness, so a HCCP certification is a must.
